br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;/rabbits -&gt; the link I&#39;m provided with&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;/rabbits/=
brown_one -&gt; the one I need to PUT to&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Let&#39;s con=
sider Case A:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The brown_one resource exists. It&#39;s =
