rown_one resource doesn&#39;t exist yet. It&#39;s not listed on the rabbits resourc=
e. The standard one perhaps is to fill up a form on /rabbits to create a ne=
w one. If it&#39;s done right, it&#39;s gonna be a POST to the current resource (/r=
abbits).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;A better form however, should have allowe=
