rm (it&#39;s supposed to work whether or not there exists a brown_one in the fi=
rst place). A third but not so great solution is to have some resource that=
 can offer up a link to something that may not exist yet -- there&#39;s gonna b=
e a /rabbits/brown_one link somehow but GET-ting it is gonna be a 404 while=
 a form is being made available if I want to fill it up.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/di=
